{"tid":806481,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG] 狼人Spyfall牛頭王Avalon Larp 遊戲Group","createTime":"2018-09-04T16:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-11T04:20:12.000Z","uid":86102,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8403b4db42b7bd4c7fa25741765409971f9aec31","tid":806481,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T16:50:59.000Z","msg":"燈燈燈櫈 又係我<br />\n啱清左啲潛水人員 宜家希望你都可以加入一齊玩啦<br />\n下面呢堆野照copy 唔好介意<br />\n<br />\n宜家telegram狼人新增左啲新角色<br />\n仲新出好多唔同既Game Bot 有唔同既game玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果你都想玩Game可以放鬆下就一齊加入啦<br />\n包括有avalon, 31點, 狼人, 牛頭王 同標題講個啲 等等<br />\n<br />\n另帶一提既就係Larp<br />\n唔知larp係咩 唔緊要 佢係一種角色扮演推理遊戲<br />\n宜家香港都有真人larp玩 但我地group主要用discord玩網上劇本<br />\n簡單黎講 有單案件 有個兇手 同一堆嫌疑犯 <br />\n每人扮演一個角色 大家都收到份劇本<br />\n透過問答 查屍體或現場去推理兇手咁<br />\n有興趣既可以一齊玩!!!<br />\n<br />\n最後係到我想講真心想玩遊戲既就入group啦<br />\n唔怕你唔識 零認識新手入黎玩都得<br />\n但唔好入到黎就一直潛水任何game都唔玩<br />\n我真係好希望大家都可以享受玩遊戲<br />\n所以想入就pm我啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/whylookatme\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwhylookatme&d=x89%2FcoWTpXmQxXKwNzv8If1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1a1d9446\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/whylookatme</a>"},{"pid":"3e48933b33cdc391427c7c69094a001928579c1b","tid":806481,"uid":199291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T01:22:28.000Z","msg":"check pm"},{"pid":"390b0e2fca3fad90df1da7c5377faeb1f3e6da62","tid":806481,"uid":199291,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T07:47:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b82d674489cb6f9e05b85d71146477597c95ae3e","tid":806481,"uid":199291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T06:13:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e60ca5acfba78f90c3500256f91202ce5aeb915","tid":806481,"uid":86102,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"r